item.title: Post 2
item.description: The unconventional guide to hidden object games. Why do people think football games are a good idea? What everyone is saying about custom playing cards. The 20 worst songs about football games. 18 myths uncovered about virtual lives. Why do people think driving games are a good idea? Why the world would end without multiplayer games. Expose: you’re losing money by not using football games. How video game designers aren’t as bad as you think. 19 podcasts about game websites.
